<p>在【IT之家】发送【 <span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">升级</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;">】</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">立刻将iPhone升级到 iOS 14。</span></p>
<p><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">▼</span></strong></span></p>
